description: Alexa will prompt you with a command line command (sometimes spelled out), like, "what is C D ?".  Then you answer what that means in english (as a human, not computer) by answering the multiple choice.  Ten total questions, try to get a perfect 10.
name: Command Line Basics
shortDescription: Test your knowledge of the command line (linux).  Tell Alexa what the command line command means in common (human) terms.  Just answer the multiple choice.
